0:22:19.640,0:22:27.780
Nyaraka hizi haipaswi kuonekana na mtu mwingine yeyote. Ni kati yako, mimi na Mungu tu.

0:22:27.780,0:22:31.800
Hebu nioneshe moja tu kwa sababu ya kile kilichotokea.

0:22:31.800,0:22:32.760
moja tu.

0:22:32.760,0:22:39.060
Nataka mtu mmoja aje asome nyaraka hii.

0:22:39.060,0:22:40.680
Na picha.

0:22:40.680,0:22:49.860
